text: Yinchuan Township () is a township under the administration of Jishishan Bonan, Dongxiang and Salar Autonomous County, Gansu, China. , it has 12 villages under its administration. == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Gansu Category:Jishishan Bonan, Dongxiang and Salar Autonomous County
